== Deaths == * Year 10 of {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (Gregorian calendar {{ill|October 26|ja|10月26日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , [[1633]] ) – {{ill|Horio Tadaharu|ja|堀尾忠晴|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , lord of {{ill|Matsue Domain|ja|松江藩|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (b. [[1599]] ). * Year 1 of {{ill|Kyōhō|ja|享保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (Gregorian calendar {{ill|November 7|ja|11月7日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , [[1716]] ) – {{ill|Prince Arisugawa no Miya Masahito|ja|有栖川宮正仁親王|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , 4th head of the {{ill|Arisugawa-no-miya|ja|有栖川宮|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (b. [[1694]] ). * Year 7 of Kyōhō (Gregorian calendar {{ill|November 2|ja|11月2日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , [[1722]] ) – {{ill|Ikenishi Gonsui|ja|池西言水|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , {{ill|haiku poet|ja|Haiku Poet|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (b. [[1650]] ). * Year 9 of Kyōhō (Gregorian calendar {{ill|November 9|ja|11月9日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , [[1724]] ) – {{ill|Nishikawa Joken|ja|西川如見|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , {{ill|astronomer|ja|天文学者|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (b. [[1648]] ). * Year 1 of {{ill|Enkyō|ja|Enkyō|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (Gregorian calendar {{ill|October 29|ja|10月29日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , [[1744]] ) – {{ill|Ishida Baigan|ja|石田梅岩|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , {{ill|philosopher|ja|Thinker|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (b. [[1685]] ). * Year 6 of {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (Gregorian calendar {{ill|November 14|ja|11月14日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , [[1859]] ) – {{ill|Satō Issai|ja|佐藤一斎|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , {{ill|Confucian scholar|ja|1=Ru (Confucian scholar)|儒学者|zh|儒生|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (b. [[1772]] ).
