{{Lunisolar September}} '''September 24''' is the 24th day of month {{ill|September (Lunisolar)|ja|9月 (旧暦)|lt=September|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} the 9th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} day is {{ill|Tomobiki|ja|友引|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . == Events == * Year 19 of {{ill|Keichō|ja|Keichō|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (Gregorian calendar {{ill|October 27|ja|10月27日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , [[1614]] ) – The {{ill|Edo shogunate|ja|Tokugawa shogunate|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} banishes {{ill|Takayama Ukon|ja|高山右近|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and 148 {{ill|Kirishitan daimyō|ja|Christian Daimyō|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} to {{ill|Manila|ja|マニラ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and {{ill|Macau|ja|マカオ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . * Year 3 of {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (Gregorian calendar {{ill|October 18|ja|10月18日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , [[1870]] ) – The {{ill|Dajōkan|ja|太政官|1=Daijō-kan|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} issues a decree regarding the statistical reports of prefectural products, which later becomes the basis for {{ill|Statistics Day|ja|統計の日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} .
== Births == * Year 1 of {{ill|Longde (Later Liang)|ja|龍徳 (五代後梁)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (Julian calendar {{ill|October 27|ja|10月27日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , [[921]] ) – {{ill|Chai Rong|ja|柴栄|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , known as Emperor Shizong, the second emperor of {{ill|Later Zhou|ja|後周|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (d. [[959]] ). * Year 4 of {{ill|Hongzhi Emperor|ja|Kōji (明)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (Julian calendar {{ill|October 26|ja|10月26日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , [[1491]] ) – The {{ill|Zhengde Emperor|ja|正徳帝|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the 11th emperor of the {{ill|Ming dynasty|ja|明|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (d. [[1521]] ). * Year 2 of {{ill|Tenbun|ja|天文 (元号)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (Julian calendar {{ill|October 12|ja|10月12日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , [[1533]] ) – {{ill|Asakura Yoshikage|ja|朝倉義景|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , {{ill|Sengoku daimyō|ja|戦国大名|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (d. [[1573]] )<ref>{{Kotobank|朝倉義景}} </ref>. * Year 8 of {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (Gregorian calendar {{ill|October 23|ja|10月23日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , [[1837]] ) – {{ill|Ōkura Kihachirō|ja|大倉喜八郎|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , businessman and founder of the {{ill|Ōkura zaibatsu|ja|大倉財閥|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (d. [[1928]] ). * Year 6 of {{ill|Kaei|ja|嘉永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (Gregorian calendar {{ill|October 26|ja|10月26日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , [[1853]] ) – {{ill|Tokugawa Akitake|ja|徳川昭武|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , last lord of the {{ill|Mito Domain|ja|Mito Domain|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (d. [[1910]] ).
== Deaths == * Year 10 of {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (Gregorian calendar {{ill|October 26|ja|10月26日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , [[1633]] ) – {{ill|Horio Tadaharu|ja|堀尾忠晴|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , lord of {{ill|Matsue Domain|ja|松江藩|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (b. [[1599]] ). * Year 1 of {{ill|Kyōhō|ja|享保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (Gregorian calendar {{ill|November 7|ja|11月7日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , [[1716]] ) – {{ill|Prince Arisugawa no Miya Masahito|ja|有栖川宮正仁親王|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , 4th head of the {{ill|Arisugawa-no-miya|ja|有栖川宮|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (b. [[1694]] ). * Year 7 of Kyōhō (Gregorian calendar {{ill|November 2|ja|11月2日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , [[1722]] ) – {{ill|Ikenishi Gonsui|ja|池西言水|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , {{ill|haiku poet|ja|Haiku Poet|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (b. [[1650]] ). * Year 9 of Kyōhō (Gregorian calendar {{ill|November 9|ja|11月9日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , [[1724]] ) – {{ill|Nishikawa Joken|ja|西川如見|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , {{ill|astronomer|ja|天文学者|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (b. [[1648]] ). * Year 1 of {{ill|Enkyō|ja|Enkyō|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (Gregorian calendar {{ill|October 29|ja|10月29日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , [[1744]] ) – {{ill|Ishida Baigan|ja|石田梅岩|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , {{ill|philosopher|ja|Thinker|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (b. [[1685]] ). * Year 6 of {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (Gregorian calendar {{ill|November 14|ja|11月14日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , [[1859]] ) – {{ill|Satō Issai|ja|佐藤一斎|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , {{ill|Confucian scholar|ja|1=Ru (Confucian scholar)|儒学者|zh|儒生|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (b. [[1772]] ).
