== Events ==
* Year 19 of {{ill|Keichō|ja|Keichō|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  (Gregorian calendar {{ill|October 27|ja|10月27日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , [[1614]] ) – The {{ill|Edo shogunate|ja|Tokugawa shogunate|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  banishes {{ill|Takayama Ukon|ja|高山右近|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  and 148 {{ill|Kirishitan daimyō|ja|Christian Daimyō|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  to {{ill|Manila|ja|マニラ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  and {{ill|Macau|ja|マカオ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} .
* Year 3 of {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  (Gregorian calendar {{ill|October 18|ja|10月18日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , [[1870]] ) – The {{ill|Dajōkan|ja|太政官|1=Daijō-kan|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  issues a decree regarding the statistical reports of prefectural products, which later becomes the basis for {{ill|Statistics Day|ja|統計の日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} .

== Births ==
* Year 1 of {{ill|Longde (Later Liang)|ja|龍徳 (五代後梁)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  (Julian calendar {{ill|October 27|ja|10月27日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , [[921]] ) – {{ill|Chai Rong|ja|柴栄|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , known as Emperor Shizong, the second emperor of {{ill|Later Zhou|ja|後周|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  (d. [[959]] ).
* Year 4 of {{ill|Hongzhi Emperor|ja|Kōji (明)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  (Julian calendar {{ill|October 26|ja|10月26日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , [[1491]] ) – The {{ill|Zhengde Emperor|ja|正徳帝|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , the 11th emperor of the {{ill|Ming dynasty|ja|明|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  (d. [[1521]] ).
* Year 2 of {{ill|Tenbun|ja|天文 (元号)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  (Julian calendar {{ill|October 12|ja|10月12日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , [[1533]] ) – {{ill|Asakura Yoshikage|ja|朝倉義景|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , {{ill|Sengoku daimyō|ja|戦国大名|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  (d. [[1573]] )<ref>{{Kotobank|朝倉義景|qq=}} </ref>.
* Year 8 of {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  (Gregorian calendar {{ill|October 23|ja|10月23日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , [[1837]] ) – {{ill|Ōkura Kihachirō|ja|大倉喜八郎|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , businessman and founder of the {{ill|Ōkura zaibatsu|ja|大倉財閥|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  (d. [[1928]] ).
* Year 6 of {{ill|Kaei|ja|嘉永|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  (Gregorian calendar {{ill|October 26|ja|10月26日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , [[1853]] ) – {{ill|Tokugawa Akitake|ja|徳川昭武|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , last lord of the {{ill|Mito Domain|ja|Mito Domain|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  (d. [[1910]] ).

== Deaths ==
* Year 10 of {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  (Gregorian calendar {{ill|October 26|ja|10月26日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , [[1633]] ) – {{ill|Horio Tadaharu|ja|堀尾忠晴|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , lord of {{ill|Matsue Domain|ja|松江藩|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  (b. [[1599]] ).
* Year 1 of {{ill|Kyōhō|ja|享保|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  (Gregorian calendar {{ill|November 7|ja|11月7日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , [[1716]] ) – {{ill|Prince Arisugawa no Miya Masahito|ja|有栖川宮正仁親王|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , 4th head of the {{ill|Arisugawa-no-miya|ja|有栖川宮|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  (b. [[1694]] ).
* Year 7 of Kyōhō (Gregorian calendar {{ill|November 2|ja|11月2日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , [[1722]] ) – {{ill|Ikenishi Gonsui|ja|池西言水|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , {{ill|haiku poet|ja|Haiku Poet|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  (b. [[1650]] ).
* Year 9 of Kyōhō (Gregorian calendar {{ill|November 9|ja|11月9日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , [[1724]] ) – {{ill|Nishikawa Joken|ja|西川如見|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , {{ill|astronomer|ja|天文学者|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  (b. [[1648]] ).
* Year 1 of {{ill|Enkyō|ja|Enkyō|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  (Gregorian calendar {{ill|October 29|ja|10月29日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , [[1744]] ) – {{ill|Ishida Baigan|ja|石田梅岩|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , {{ill|philosopher|ja|Thinker|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  (b. [[1685]] ).
* Year 6 of {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  (Gregorian calendar {{ill|November 14|ja|11月14日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , [[1859]] ) – {{ill|Satō Issai|ja|佐藤一斎|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , {{ill|Confucian scholar|ja|1=Ru (Confucian scholar)|儒学者|zh|儒生|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  (b. [[1772]] ).


