== Births == * Year 1 of {{ill|Longde (Later Liang)|ja|龍徳 (五代後梁)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Longde (Later Liang)|qq=}} (Julian calendar {{ill|October 27|ja|10月27日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 27|qq=}} , [[921]] ) – {{ill|Chai Rong|ja|柴栄|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Chai Rong|qq=}} , known as Emperor Shizong, the second emperor of {{ill|Later Zhou|ja|後周|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Later Zhou|qq=}} (d. [[959]] ). * Year 4 of {{ill|Hongzhi Emperor|ja|Kōji (明)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hongzhi Emperor|qq=}} (Julian calendar {{ill|October 26|ja|10月26日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 26|qq=}} , [[1491]] ) – The {{ill|Zhengde Emperor|ja|正徳帝|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Zhengde Emperor|qq=}} , the 11th emperor of the {{ill|Ming dynasty|ja|明|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ming dynasty|qq=}} (d. [[1521]] ). * Year 2 of {{ill|Tenbun|ja|天文 (元号)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenbun|qq=}} (Julian calendar {{ill|October 12|ja|10月12日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 12|qq=}} , [[1533]] ) – {{ill|Asakura Yoshikage|ja|朝倉義景|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Asakura Yoshikage|qq=}} , {{ill|Sengoku daimyō|ja|戦国大名|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sengoku daimyō|qq=}} (d. [[1573]] )<ref>{{Kotobank|朝倉義景|qq=}} </ref>. * Year 8 of {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenpō|qq=}} (Gregorian calendar {{ill|October 23|ja|10月23日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 23|qq=}} , [[1837]] ) – {{ill|Ōkura Kihachirō|ja|大倉喜八郎|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōkura Kihachirō|qq=}} , businessman and founder of the {{ill|Ōkura zaibatsu|ja|大倉財閥|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōkura zaibatsu|qq=}} (d. [[1928]] ). * Year 6 of {{ill|Kaei|ja|嘉永|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kaei|qq=}} (Gregorian calendar {{ill|October 26|ja|10月26日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 26|qq=}} , [[1853]] ) – {{ill|Tokugawa Akitake|ja|徳川昭武|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokugawa Akitake|qq=}} , last lord of the {{ill|Mito Domain|ja|Mito Domain|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mito Domain|qq=}} (d. [[1910]] ).
== Deaths == * Year 10 of {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kan'ei|qq=}} (Gregorian calendar {{ill|October 26|ja|10月26日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 26|qq=}} , [[1633]] ) – {{ill|Horio Tadaharu|ja|堀尾忠晴|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Horio Tadaharu|qq=}} , lord of {{ill|Matsue Domain|ja|松江藩|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Matsue Domain|qq=}} (b. [[1599]] ). * Year 1 of {{ill|Kyōhō|ja|享保|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kyōhō|qq=}} (Gregorian calendar {{ill|November 7|ja|11月7日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 7|qq=}} , [[1716]] ) – {{ill|Prince Arisugawa no Miya Masahito|ja|有栖川宮正仁親王|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Prince Arisugawa no Miya Masahito|qq=}} , 4th head of the {{ill|Arisugawa-no-miya|ja|有栖川宮|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Arisugawa-no-miya|qq=}} (b. [[1694]] ). * Year 7 of Kyōhō (Gregorian calendar {{ill|November 2|ja|11月2日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 2|qq=}} , [[1722]] ) – {{ill|Ikenishi Gonsui|ja|池西言水|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ikenishi Gonsui|qq=}} , {{ill|haiku poet|ja|Haiku Poet|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/haiku poet|qq=}} (b. [[1650]] ). * Year 9 of Kyōhō (Gregorian calendar {{ill|November 9|ja|11月9日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 9|qq=}} , [[1724]] ) – {{ill|Nishikawa Joken|ja|西川如見|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Nishikawa Joken|qq=}} , {{ill|astronomer|ja|天文学者|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/astronomer|qq=}} (b. [[1648]] ). * Year 1 of {{ill|Enkyō|ja|Enkyō|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Enkyō|qq=}} (Gregorian calendar {{ill|October 29|ja|10月29日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 29|qq=}} , [[1744]] ) – {{ill|Ishida Baigan|ja|石田梅岩|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ishida Baigan|qq=}} , {{ill|philosopher|ja|Thinker|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/philosopher|qq=}} (b. [[1685]] ). * Year 6 of {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ansei|qq=}} (Gregorian calendar {{ill|November 14|ja|11月14日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 14|qq=}} , [[1859]] ) – {{ill|Satō Issai|ja|佐藤一斎|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Satō Issai|qq=}} , {{ill|Confucian scholar|ja|1=Ru (Confucian scholar)|儒学者|zh|儒生|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Confucian scholar|13=User:Immanuelle/Ru (Confucian scholar)|qq=}} (b. [[1772]] ).
