{{afc comment|1=This article as with the other date articles is relatively limited in scope to Japan. Reviewing the translation of this is good and also adding content translated from Chinese and Korean wikipedias will also be good. Both wikipedias are also relatively centered around their own countries for their Lunisolar calendar dates[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 00:16, 28 April 2025 (UTC)}} {{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=九月廿四|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=음력 9월 24일|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar September|qq=}} '''September 24''' is the 24th day of month {{ill|September (Lunisolar)|ja|9月 (旧暦)|lt=September (Nagatsuki)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/September (Lunisolar)|qq=}} the 9th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyō|qq=}} day is {{ill|Tomobiki|ja|友引|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tomobiki|qq=}} . == Events == * Year 19 of {{ill|Keichō|1=Keichō|2=ja|3=慶長|ja|Keichō|1=Keichō|2=ja|3=慶長|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keichō|qq=}} (Gregorian calendar {{ill|October 27|ja|10月27日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 27|qq=}} , [[1614]] ) – The {{ill|Edo shogunate|ja|Tokugawa shogunate|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Edo shogunate|qq=}} banishes {{ill|Takayama Ukon|ja|高山右近|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Takayama Ukon|qq=}} and 148 {{ill|Kirishitan daimyō|ja|Christian Daimyō|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kirishitan daimyō|qq=}} to {{ill|Manila|ja|マニラ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Manila|qq=}} and {{ill|Macau|ja|マカオ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Macau|qq=}} . * Year 3 of {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji era|qq=}} (Gregorian calendar {{ill|October 18|ja|10月18日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 18|qq=}} , [[1870]] ) – The {{ill|Dajōkan|ja|太政官|1=Daijō-kan|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Dajōkan|13=User:Immanuelle/Daijō-kan|qq=}} issues a decree regarding the statistical reports of prefectural products, which later becomes the basis for {{ill|Statistics Day|ja|統計の日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Statistics Day|qq=}} .
== Births == * Year 1 of {{ill|Longde (Later Liang)|ja|龍徳 (五代後梁)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Longde (Later Liang)|qq=}} (Julian calendar {{ill|October 27|ja|10月27日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 27|qq=}} , [[921]] ) – {{ill|Chai Rong|ja|柴栄|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Chai Rong|qq=}} , known as Emperor Shizong, the second emperor of {{ill|Later Zhou|ja|後周|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Later Zhou|qq=}} (d. [[959]] ). * Year 4 of {{ill|Hongzhi Emperor|ja|Kōji (明)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hongzhi Emperor|qq=}} (Julian calendar {{ill|October 26|ja|10月26日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 26|qq=}} , [[1491]] ) – The {{ill|Zhengde Emperor|ja|正徳帝|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Zhengde Emperor|qq=}} , the 11th emperor of the {{ill|Ming dynasty|ja|明|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ming dynasty|qq=}} (d. [[1521]] ). * Year 2 of {{ill|Tenbun|ja|天文 (元号)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenbun|qq=}} (Julian calendar {{ill|October 12|ja|10月12日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 12|qq=}} , [[1533]] ) – {{ill|Asakura Yoshikage|ja|朝倉義景|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Asakura Yoshikage|qq=}} , {{ill|Sengoku daimyō|ja|戦国大名|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sengoku daimyō|qq=}} (d. [[1573]] )<ref>{{Kotobank|朝倉義景|qq=}} </ref>. * Year 8 of {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenpō|qq=}} (Gregorian calendar {{ill|October 23|ja|10月23日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 23|qq=}} , [[1837]] ) – {{ill|Ōkura Kihachirō|ja|大倉喜八郎|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōkura Kihachirō|qq=}} , businessman and founder of the {{ill|Ōkura zaibatsu|ja|大倉財閥|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōkura zaibatsu|qq=}} (d. [[1928]] ). * Year 6 of {{ill|Kaei|ja|嘉永|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kaei|qq=}} (Gregorian calendar {{ill|October 26|ja|10月26日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 26|qq=}} , [[1853]] ) – {{ill|Tokugawa Akitake|ja|徳川昭武|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokugawa Akitake|qq=}} , last lord of the {{ill|Mito Domain|1=Mito Domain|2=ja|3=水戸藩|ja|Mito Domain|1=Mito Domain|2=ja|3=水戸藩|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mito Domain|qq=}} (d. [[1910]] ).
== Deaths == * Year 10 of {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kan'ei|qq=}} (Gregorian calendar {{ill|October 26|ja|10月26日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 26|qq=}} , [[1633]] ) – {{ill|Horio Tadaharu|ja|堀尾忠晴|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Horio Tadaharu|qq=}} , lord of {{ill|Matsue Domain|ja|松江藩|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Matsue Domain|qq=}} (b. [[1599]] ). * Year 1 of {{ill|Kyōhō|ja|享保|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kyōhō|qq=}} (Gregorian calendar {{ill|November 7|ja|11月7日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 7|qq=}} , [[1716]] ) – {{ill|Prince Arisugawa no Miya Masahito|ja|有栖川宮正仁親王|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Prince Arisugawa no Miya Masahito|qq=}} , 4th head of the {{ill|Arisugawa-no-miya|ja|有栖川宮|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Arisugawa-no-miya|qq=}} (b. [[1694]] ). * Year 7 of Kyōhō (Gregorian calendar {{ill|November 2|ja|11月2日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 2|qq=}} , [[1722]] ) – {{ill|Ikenishi Gonsui|ja|池西言水|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ikenishi Gonsui|qq=}} , {{ill|haiku poet|ja|Haiku Poet|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/haiku poet|qq=}} (b. [[1650]] ). * Year 9 of Kyōhō (Gregorian calendar {{ill|November 9|ja|11月9日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 9|qq=}} , [[1724]] ) – {{ill|Nishikawa Joken|ja|西川如見|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Nishikawa Joken|qq=}} , {{ill|astronomer|ja|天文学者|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/astronomer|qq=}} (b. [[1648]] ). * Year 1 of {{ill|Enkyō|ja|Enkyō|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Enkyō|qq=}} (Gregorian calendar {{ill|October 29|ja|10月29日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 29|qq=}} , [[1744]] ) – {{ill|Ishida Baigan|ja|石田梅岩|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ishida Baigan|qq=}} , {{ill|philosopher|ja|Thinker|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/philosopher|qq=}} (b. [[1685]] ). * Year 6 of {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ansei|qq=}} (Gregorian calendar {{ill|November 14|ja|11月14日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 14|qq=}} , [[1859]] ) – {{ill|Satō Issai|ja|佐藤一斎|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Satō Issai|qq=}} , {{ill|Confucian scholar|ja|1=Ru (Confucian scholar)|儒学者|zh|儒生|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Confucian scholar|13=User:Immanuelle/Ru (Confucian scholar)|qq=}} (b. [[1772]] ).
