== Births == * Year 1 of {{ill|Longde (Later Liang)|ja|龍徳 (五代後梁)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Longde (Later Liang)|qq=}} (Julian calendar [[:en:October 27|October 27]] , [[921]] ) – [[:en:Chai Rong|Chai Rong]] , known as Emperor Shizong, the second emperor of [[:en:Later Zhou|Later Zhou]] (d. [[959]] ). * Year 4 of {{ill|Hongzhi Emperor|ja|Kōji (明)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hongzhi Emperor|qq=}} (Julian calendar [[:en:October 26|October 26]] , [[1491]] ) – The [[:en:Zhengde Emperor|Zhengde Emperor]] , the 11th emperor of the [[:en:Ming dynasty|Ming dynasty]] (d. [[1521]] ). * Year 2 of [[:en:Tenbun|Tenbun]] (Julian calendar [[:en:October 12|October 12]] , [[1533]] ) – [[:en:Asakura Yoshikage|Asakura Yoshikage]] , {{ill|Sengoku daimyō|ja|戦国大名|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sengoku daimyō|qq=}} (d. [[1573]] )<ref>{{Kotobank|朝倉義景|qq=}} </ref>. * Year 8 of [[:en:Tenpō|Tenpō]] (Gregorian calendar [[:en:October 23|October 23]] , [[1837]] ) – [[:en:Ōkura Kihachirō|Ōkura Kihachirō]] , businessman and founder of the {{ill|Ōkura zaibatsu|ja|大倉財閥|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōkura zaibatsu|qq=}} (d. [[1928]] ). * Year 6 of [[:en:Kaei|Kaei]] (Gregorian calendar [[:en:October 26|October 26]] , [[1853]] ) – [[:en:Tokugawa Akitake|Tokugawa Akitake]] , last lord of the {{ill|Mito Domain|1=Mito Domain|2=ja|3=水戸藩|ja|Mito Domain|1=Mito Domain|2=ja|3=水戸藩|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mito Domain|qq=}} (d. [[1910]] ).
== Deaths == * Year 10 of [[:en:Kan'ei|Kan'ei]] (Gregorian calendar [[:en:October 26|October 26]] , [[1633]] ) – [[:en:Horio Tadaharu|Horio Tadaharu]] , lord of [[:en:Matsue Domain|Matsue Domain]] (b. [[1599]] ). * Year 1 of [[:en:Kyōhō|Kyōhō]] (Gregorian calendar [[:en:November 7|November 7]] , [[1716]] ) – {{ill|Prince Arisugawa no Miya Masahito|ja|有栖川宮正仁親王|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Prince Arisugawa no Miya Masahito|qq=}} , 4th head of the [[:en:Arisugawa-no-miya|Arisugawa-no-miya]] (b. [[1694]] ). * Year 7 of Kyōhō (Gregorian calendar [[:en:November 2|November 2]] , [[1722]] ) – {{ill|Ikenishi Gonsui|ja|池西言水|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ikenishi Gonsui|qq=}} , {{ill|haiku poet|ja|Haiku Poet|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/haiku poet|qq=}} (b. [[1650]] ). * Year 9 of Kyōhō (Gregorian calendar [[:en:November 9|November 9]] , [[1724]] ) – [[:en:Nishikawa Joken|Nishikawa Joken]] , [[:en:Astronomer|astronomer]] (b. [[1648]] ). * Year 1 of {{ill|Enkyō|ja|Enkyō|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Enkyō|qq=}} (Gregorian calendar [[:en:October 29|October 29]] , [[1744]] ) – [[:en:Ishida Baigan|Ishida Baigan]] , {{ill|philosopher|ja|Thinker|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/philosopher|qq=}} (b. [[1685]] ). * Year 6 of [[:en:Ansei|Ansei]] (Gregorian calendar [[:en:November 14|November 14]] , [[1859]] ) – [[:en:Satō Issai|Satō Issai]] , {{ill|Confucian scholar|ja|1=Ru (Confucian scholar)|儒学者|zh|儒生|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Confucian scholar|13=User:Immanuelle/Ru (Confucian scholar)|qq=}} (b. [[1772]] ).
