== Deaths == * Year 10 of [[:en:Kan'ei|Kan'ei]] (Gregorian calendar [[:en:October 26|October 26]] , [[:en:1633|1633]] ) – [[:en:Horio Tadaharu|Horio Tadaharu]] , lord of [[:en:Matsue Domain|Matsue Domain]] (b. [[:en:1599|1599]] ). * Year 1 of [[:en:Kyōhō|Kyōhō]] (Gregorian calendar [[:en:November 7|November 7]] , [[:en:1716|1716]] ) – {{ill|Prince Arisugawa no Miya Masahito|ja|有栖川宮正仁親王|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Prince Arisugawa no Miya Masahito|qq=|1=Arisugawa-no-miya Tadahito-shinnō|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q11516504}} , 4th head of the [[:en:Arisugawa-no-miya|Arisugawa-no-miya]] (b. [[:en:1694|1694]] ). * Year 7 of Kyōhō (Gregorian calendar [[:en:November 2|November 2]] , [[:en:1722|1722]] ) – {{ill|Ikenishi Gonsui|ja|池西言水|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ikenishi Gonsui|qq=|1=Ikenishi Gonsui|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q11552255}} , {{ill|haiku poet|ja|Haiku Poet|1=Haiku poet|2=ja|3=俳句詩人|1=Haiku Poet|2=ja|3=俳句詩人|qid=Q135490197|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/haiku poet|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} (b. [[:en:1650|1650]] ). * Year 9 of Kyōhō (Gregorian calendar [[:en:November 9|November 9]] , [[:en:1724|1724]] ) – [[:en:Nishikawa Joken|Nishikawa Joken]] , [[:en:Astronomer|astronomer]] (b. [[:en:1648|1648]] ). * Year 1 of {{ill|Enkyō|1=Enkyō|2=ja|3=延享|lt=Enkyō|ja|Enkyō|1=Enkyō (Edo period)|2=ja|3=延享|lt=Enkyō|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Enkyō|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q1183728}} (Gregorian calendar [[:en:October 29|October 29]] , [[:en:1744|1744]] ) – [[:en:Ishida Baigan|Ishida Baigan]] , {{ill|philosopher|ja|Thinker|1=thinker|2=ja|3=思想家|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/philosopher|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q24885626}} (b. [[:en:1685|1685]] ). * Year 6 of [[:en:Ansei|Ansei]] (Gregorian calendar [[:en:November 14|November 14]] , [[:en:1859|1859]] ) – [[:en:Satō Issai|Satō Issai]] , {{ill|Confucian scholar|ja|1=Ru (Confucian scholar)|儒学者|zh|儒生|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Confucian scholar|13=User:Immanuelle/Ru (Confucian scholar)|qq=}} (b. [[:en:1772|1772]] ).
